                  <p class="ia-table-text"><b>Option 1 (preferred):</b> A reform package that requires primary legislation more closely aligning Limited Partnership transparency requirements to those of companies</p>
                  <p class="ia-table-text"><b>Option 2</b>: A non-legislative option of additional guidance for limited partnerships to ensure complete and accurate reporting</p>
                  <p class="ia-table-text">Option 1 is the only option comprehensive enough to achieve the policy objectives</p>
